## Extensions.registerMixin() function

Registers a new extension function that adds all key/value of mixinObj.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare function registerMixin(name: string, mixinObj: AnyDuringMigration): void;
```

## Parameters

|  Parameter | Type | Description |
|  --- | --- | --- |
|  name | string | The name of this extension. |
|  mixinObj | AnyDuringMigration | The values to mix in. |

<b>Returns:</b>

void

## Exceptions

{<!-- -->Error<!-- -->} if the extension name is empty or the extension is already registered.
